     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts FRSectionImmunizationsLMCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"FRSectionImmunizationsLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcFRSectionImmunizationsLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-vaccinations</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-vaccinations</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMVaccinations</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAVaccinations</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMVaccinations.codeSection</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAVaccinations.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMVaccinations.titreSection</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAVaccinations.title</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMVaccinations.blocNarratif</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAVaccinations.text</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMVaccinations.entree.vaccinations</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAVaccinations.entry.FRCDAVaccination</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Groupe 2 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-vaccinations</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-composition-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAVaccinations</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCompositionDocument.section:immunizations</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAVaccinations.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCompositionDocument.section:immunizations.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAVaccinations.title</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCompositionDocument.section:immunizations.title</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAVaccinations.text</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCompositionDocument.section:immunizations.text</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAVaccinations.entry.FRCDAVaccination</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCompositionDocument.section:immunizations.entry:FRImmunizationDocument</td></tr></table></div>"
